headline: More Affordable Housing: Regions Bank Appoints Chase Simpson as Relationship Manager Serving Clients in Several States
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., November 20, 2024--Regions Bank on Wednesday announced Chase Simpson has been named vice president and relationship manager in the Regions Affordable Housing division.
